{"tid":2323250,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女團 GFRIEND 忙內 Umji 嚴智，因「腿部肌肉受傷」將暫停活動！","createTime":"2020-12-13T04:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T13:06:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"90818ac13728a1efae48b77895b49c841773a9bc","tid":2323250,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_59246badef55d39bfdd5ad4ba75c8d2f/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-13/132286-888712.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_59246badef55d39bfdd5ad4ba75c8d2f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-13%2F132286-888712.jpg&h=35338488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可愛的嚴智妹妹，好好休息啊～！TAT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最新消息，人氣女團 GFRIEND 的忙內 Umji 嚴智因受傷等健康問題，將暫時不參加團體的活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a86508e57d9e5bf9387c7707a7b748db/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-13/132286-888713.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a86508e57d9e5bf9387c7707a7b748db%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-13%2F132286-888713.jpg&h=4bd1aa14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天早上，GFRIEND 所屬的 Source Music 經紀公司表示：「嚴智最近因腿部疼痛而到醫院檢查，被診斷出腿部肌肉及肌腱受損，為了恢復會需要充分的休息與治療，所以決定暫時不參加團體的行程。這是優先考慮嚴智健康情況所做出的決定，希望粉絲們能夠諒解。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e25c525fbcc5b9bb7b51964f0d6de356/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-13/132286-888714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e25c525fbcc5b9bb7b51964f0d6de356%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-13%2F132286-888714.jpg&h=15be1355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前正是偶像在年末舞台上展現各種面貌的時刻，對此消息也感到非常遺憾，同時也希望嚴智能夠好好休息，盡快好起來再次和粉絲們見面～！<br />\n<br />\n（圖：GFRIEND．FB）"},{"pid":"1167f8a5a9ba626bbc44d1df9d1579983ef250d4","tid":2323250,"uid":107913,"like":6,"dislike":14,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T04:56:24.000Z","msg":"差唔多時間啦, 好似差佢未改造"},{"pid":"785